defaultorder
default:
defaultIn each case, an 
defaultorder
default may be made only if it appears to the Secretary of State that the body regulates the practice of a profession and maintains and enforces rules for ensuring that its insolvency specialist members are fit and proper persons to act as insolvency practitioners and meet acceptable requirements as to education practical training and experience.   An 
defaultorder
