default89.
default&#xa0; 
defaultThe powers to recognise professional bodies which may authorise their members to act as an insolvency practitioner and to revoke a body’s recognition in section 391 have been delegated since the Insolvency Act 1986 came into effect.  The clause will replace these powers with powers enabling the 
defaultdepartment
