default&#xa0;
default345.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis power is exercisable in relation to England and Wales, Scotland and Northern Ireland and includes power to amend legislation passed or made by the devolved legislatures. Any amendments would, however, be consequential on other provisions of the Bill. Discussions as to whether a legislative consent motion is necessary are taking place.
